  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/0123c09af04d1140555c042a1dc5fbc4.avif?t=1761275726\" width=1560 height=994 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What starts with a conversation between two long lost friends spills out into a captivating tale about four youths struggling to pursue their dreams and find their place in the world as love complicates everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this coming-of-age, slice-of-life drama, you'll immerse yourself into the stories of an artist trying to balance his budding career and final years of school, a free-spirited woman seeking something that can hold her interest, a proud female athlete, and an aspiring film-maker, as they navigate the hurdles of their dreams and the way love begins changing their relationships with each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the classic tale that spawned the acclaimed anime for yourself.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/8ec0fc23ab6fceccc63ce6d820961617.avif?t=1761275726\" width=1560 height=426 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/71dd99af71278b2aae0bef4839f5269d.poster.avif?t=1761275726\" width=780 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/71dd99af71278b2aae0bef4839f5269d.webm?t=1761275726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ef utilizes over a thousand CG, animated expressions, lip synch, along with careful, detailed production and direction to create a truly cinematic experience rarely found in visual novels.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/5f87b1278eca32955ed22fcb885fd9c4.poster.avif?t=1761275726\" width=780 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/5f87b1278eca32955ed22fcb885fd9c4.webm?t=1761275726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The complicated relationships between the characters unfolds into a truly relatable drama with ups and downs, joys and heartaches, and a love story that will stick with you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/a8c80077710e6a2c68477e24fd775329.poster.avif?t=1761275726\" width=780 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/a8c80077710e6a2c68477e24fd775329.webm?t=1761275726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll get to see the stories being woven from the POV of all four main characters, adding to their depth and providing you a broader view of their growth and development throughout these tales.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/0123c09af04d1140555c042a1dc5fbc4.avif?t=1761275726\" width=1560 height=994 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What starts with a conversation between two long lost friends spills out into a captivating tale about four youths struggling to pursue their dreams and find their place in the world as love complicates everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this coming-of-age, slice-of-life drama, you'll immerse yourself into the stories of an artist trying to balance his budding career and final years of school, a free-spirited woman seeking something that can hold her interest, a proud female athlete, and an aspiring film-maker, as they navigate the hurdles of their dreams and the way love begins changing their relationships with each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the classic tale that spawned the acclaimed anime for yourself.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/8ec0fc23ab6fceccc63ce6d820961617.avif?t=1761275726\" width=1560 height=426 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/71dd99af71278b2aae0bef4839f5269d.poster.avif?t=1761275726\" width=780 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/71dd99af71278b2aae0bef4839f5269d.webm?t=1761275726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ef utilizes over a thousand CG, animated expressions, lip synch, along with careful, detailed production and direction to create a truly cinematic experience rarely found in visual novels.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/5f87b1278eca32955ed22fcb885fd9c4.poster.avif?t=1761275726\" width=780 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/5f87b1278eca32955ed22fcb885fd9c4.webm?t=1761275726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The complicated relationships between the characters unfolds into a truly relatable drama with ups and downs, joys and heartaches, and a love story that will stick with you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/a8c80077710e6a2c68477e24fd775329.poster.avif?t=1761275726\" width=780 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144300/extras/a8c80077710e6a2c68477e24fd775329.webm?t=1761275726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll get to see the stories being woven from the POV of all four main characters, adding to their depth and providing you a broader view of their growth and development throughout these tales.</p>",
